OL,3,CMan charged with murder of 64 year-old
OL,4,Cfollowing assault
OL,6,FA man has been charged with the murder
OL,7,Fof a 64-year-old man following an
OL,8,Fassault in a Swansea town.
OL,10,FChristopher Cooper, 39, from the
OL,11,FMaritime Quarter, Swansea, has been
OL,12,Fcharged in connection with the death
OL,13,Fof Kelvin Evans.
OL,15,FThe assault of Mr Evans is said to
OL,16,Fhave happened at The Station Hotel in
OL,17,FGorseinon on Sunday 26 May.
