OL,6,FDetective Inspector David Butt from
OL,7,FSouth Wales Police has said: "We would
OL,8,Flike to thank the community for their
OL,9,Fassistance with this investigation.
OL,10,FChristopher Cooper will appear at
OL,11,Fcourt in due course.
OL,13,F"Mr Evans' family are aware of the new
OL,14,Fcharge, and continue to receive the
OL,15,Fsupport of specially-trained officers.
OL,17,F"We continue to appeal for any
OL,18,Fwitnesses to this incident who were
OL,19,Feither inside the Station Hotel or
OL,20,Foutside the property."
