OL,6,FMr Evans' family has said: "We are
OL,7,Fdevastated at the tragic and senseless
OL,8,Floss of our wonderful, loving, funny
OL,9,Fson, brother, uncle, and friend to so
OL,10,Fmany.
OL,12,F"We are trying to come to terms with
OL,13,Fthis whole situation and ask that we
OL,14,Fare given time to grieve in private as
OL,15,Fa family."
OL,17,FAnyone with information is being asked
OL,18,Fcan contact South Wales Police quoting
OL,19,Freference: 2400172904.
